<plot>When Heroes Die is an ambient and internal piece about the effects of Post Traumatic Stress Disorder on the wife of a fallen firefighter. Shot and produced in an open and free-flowing manner with no budget, the goal of the film was to experiment with production. The result is a piece that offers much under the surface interwoven with a strong musical score.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?652847</url></doc>
